name: Able Health
long_description: Able Health is the one platform physician organizations need to manage value-based programs. From calculating HEDIS and Medicare measures to engaging clinicians and health plans, managing value-based programs can take an army of administrators and IT staff. Able Health simplifies administration, customized to your specific programs, so you can ease today's reporting requirements and set your organization up for the future of healthcare reimbursements.
one_liner: Able Health gets doctors paid more for higher quality care
